<p class="fd-paragraph">
  An AI-powered appropriate coding module that surfaces risk-adjusted coding opportunities in real time — ensuring accurate HCC capture, closing coding gaps, and maximizing compliant revenue without additional staff burden.
</p>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">What it does</h2>
<ul class="fd-list">
  <li class="fd-list-item">Real-time HCC coding opportunity identification during and after patient encounters</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Coding gap alerts surfaced to clinicians and coders at the point of care</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Audit-ready documentation with evidence trails for every coding suggestion</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Integration with EHR data to identify historically undercoded conditions</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">Compliance-first design</h2>
<p class="fd-paragraph">
  Appropriate Coding is built around CMS guidelines and audit defensibility. Every suggestion is evidence-backed — maximizing revenue capture while maintaining full compliance.
</p>
